评论概述: Exactly what I was looking for!
评论详情: UPDATE: I have had the bag for two months and have not used it as a daily bag. Today the zipper broke. Super disappointed.  This little bag is perfect! I hate carrying a purse so often times I just opt to put everything in my pockets but, as I’m sure many ladies will agree, more often than not pants don’t have pockets or they are super small. Soooo I wanted a bag that I could easily throw the few things I carry into without a hassle. It perfectly fits my personal phone and work phone (both are iPhone 12s) my wallet, keys and vape. I have some extra room too if I wanted to add chapstick or something. I also really like that it stands on its own so I don’t have to worry about all my crap falling out when I set it down. The only down side would be that I would have liked the strap to be a little longer or adjustable but that is a super easy fix given it just clips on and off.

评论概述: Horrible Odor (Update: The seller has worked to resolve the issue, earning another star)
评论详情: The FONETTOS Punk Bag is an adorable bag and appears to be very well made.  However, it has a horrible odor of gasoline or another petroleum product.  My cat just sniffed the bag and immediately turned and ran away!  I have had it open and airing for several days and the odor hasn't improved.  I'm going to put some charcoal deodorizers in it to see it that helps.  I ordered this as a gift for our daughter, who loves all think Punk, but I can't give a gift that smells this bad.UPDATE:  The seller contacted me about the odor problem with the purse we received and worked with me to resolve the problem.  Other reviewers have not mentioned a similar problem, so the bag we received may have been an outlier.  This is a really cute bag, so I hope the seller can resolve the issue with his supplier.
